        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2909075636" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer7657044646487741416">Ottessa Moshfegh seems to be completely incapable of producing works that aren&apos;t masterpieces.</span>
  <span id="freeText7657044646487741416" style="display:none">Ottessa Moshfegh seems to be completely incapable of producing works that aren't masterpieces.</span>
  <a data-text-id="7657044646487741416" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

